title: #220: Gift of Garble (@BigJayOakerson
itunes:title: Gift of Garble with Big Jay Oakerson
description: Big Jay Oakerson had me over to his apartment to talk about the worst interviews we've been a part of. We both sat through the same horrendous interviewer at SXSW and that's what gave us the idea. Some people are really good at bringing stuff out of you. Other people, not so much.
